{"tid":2384044,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"北京批英國反覆炒作BNO問題　搬石頭砸自己腳","createTime":"2021-01-28T10:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T10:32:32.000Z","uid":230530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a468318c62f322a330d1fa40e45d6c8f6a6d5eea","tid":2384044,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:06:37.000Z","msg":"英國政府為符合BNO資格港人而設的新簽證，將於本月31日起接受申請。在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅表示，英方違背承諾，一意孤行，反覆炒作BNO問題，干預香港事務及中國內政，只會搬起石頭砸自己的腳。 趙立堅重申，對香港的光明未來充滿信心，任何勢力、任何情況都動搖不了中國政府和中國人民維護國家主權、安全，維護香港繁榮穩定，反對外部干預的決心和意志。"},{"pid":"df968340cba2655f7e1a23638c1e152ec794de47","tid":2384044,"uid":785,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:07:31.000Z","msg":"英國腳指爛未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e2e36c728fbfbd15435c830b94fbfb77b81dbd","tid":2384044,"uid":318557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6J2THYN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6J2THYN.gif&h=b754ab84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81a7bce3ded26d8804f8aad26def69eeec666095","tid":2384044,"uid":18477,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sC6khVJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsC6khVJ.gif&h=59e17eae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d1d8c288eda74254f9b4e5229b19da16d20ca77","tid":2384044,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df968340cba2655f7e1a23638c1e152ec794de47","tid":2384044,"uid":785,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:07:31.000Z","msg":"英國腳指爛未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:09:46.000Z","msg":"甩左兩隻指甲"},{"pid":"336f05265b51acd223bdfa5e02ed9