":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6J2THYN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6J2THYN.gif&h=b754ab84&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:15:11.000Z","msg":"調轉咪差唔多，中共打壓香港人權但英國都阻唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b23c18bcfafd13586744788a20f4e157b985ff","tid":2384044,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:16:23.000Z","msg":"又玩腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97541ee905739f3c6e0409e2746ed9a048f473f","tid":2384044,"uid":267283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:17:41.000Z","msg":"幾時有反制措施<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0edf89322f74a0c21cd4c08cd939529dd447c7b","tid":2384044,"uid":389613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:19:40.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">香港人用 BNO 係搬石頭砸中共春袋</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原來用 BNO 離開係 Trump 一早 set 左比中共既計時炸彈！我地更應該繼承 Trump 既精神，用 BNO 逼 Biden 同中共開戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">只要有大批香港人離開，會造成現時已經虛弱既經濟徹底崩潰，而中共強行鎖國則引來百國聯軍。</span><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本１：支共反制 BNO 會引致戰爭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[武俠小說] 因為 BNO 香港變成外交博奕戰場！Trump 偷偷地幫香港插左支定海神針迫 Biden 打柒中共！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2377934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2377934</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本２：支共比 BNO 走引致經濟崩潰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[神話故事] 中共經濟末日狂奔，BNO 就係大衛與歌利亞決戰粒石頭。港人出走成就 Trump 滅共偉業。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2380593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2380593</a><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n淨係走錢無用，人都最好走埋！！你每年最少響香港幫佢賺緊 18 萬，當一蚊都唔加你，做 45 年野係 810 萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲未計你養仔又要洗 400 萬，又未計呢個只係你份糧，仲未計香港班人渣老細用你既血同汗賺既大量財富 *班 pk 可能比1蚊你但賺緊4-5蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">絕對唔好睇少自己，你淨係個人走都搞死港共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />更重要係，你走香港班仆街藍絲要頂埋你交果做稅 (that's why 屯地波要加稅)，到時班賣港賊佢地就真係活響人間地獄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n不論你係撐 Trump 既手足、定係支持滅共既手足，今次 BNO Visa 係時候身體力行，用你對腳投票去支持 Trump 呢條滅共戰線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">多你一個好多，少你一個唔掂！你既決定將會成為世界走向正義定係腐敗既關鍵因素！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"b02da8bf8e275e74cbe11656a7369a4da0769795","tid":2384044,"uid":229977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:20:38.000Z","msg":"都未開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9787ab87f243ebdee099dd60a3c910d52d9d203","tid":2384044,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:21:23.000Z","msg":"等睇萬人空巷去領事館攪visa<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d84434bae4e3f9121995ada1c4883ce5e9a636b2","tid":2384044,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c9787ab87f243ebdee099dd60a3c910d52d9d203","tid":2384044,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:21:23.000Z","msg":"等睇萬人空巷去領事館攪visa<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:24:10.000Z","msg":"應該網上搞掂<br />\n<br />\n都2021年啦"},{"pid":"ad6ab9c680172919dce886da6aa4861ca8e08a01","tid":2384044,"uid":203491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":